Usage: saveOaBlackboxes [-help] -cell <list_of_cells> -lib <libName>
                        [-view <viewName>]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-cell <list_of_cells>          # Specifies one or more blackboxes to save
                               # (string, required)
-lib <libName>                 # Specifies the OpenAccess library to use to
                               # save the blackbox abstracts (string, required)
-view <viewName>               # Specifies the cell view to save. Default:
                               # abstract (string, optional)